{
  "stem": "14168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had booked a ticket on the track train from Berlin to Amsterdam, to leave Berlin that very night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I arrived in Berlin, went to the Dutch embassy, and asked whether I needed a transit visa to Holland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, you have a visitor's visa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I took the train, the night train, to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I gave a sigh of relief as we crossed the Dutch border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few minutes later, the train stopped and the Dutch border police came in and collected passports.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my passport came right back, and he said, we can't let you into Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, you can't let me into Holland?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have a tourist visa only.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said-- you have no transit visa, they said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, but I checked with your embassy, and they said you don't need it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just about 30 minutes ago, we got a decree-- orders from Den Haag-- the Hague-- our government-- that no emigrant with tourist visa is permitted into Holland, because they may not be able to land overseas, and then we would have to take them back.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, however, you have to get off the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll give you two days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe you have some people in Holland who can help you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My friend was unable to help me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He, himself, was a refugee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after two days, they shipped me back to Germany, into the waiting arms of the Gestapo, at Osnabruck-- O-S-N-A-B-R-U-C-K.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, the Gestapo was waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said, you know we are going to ship you straight to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You came back, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've never talked as fast in my life as I talked then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I knew my life was in the balance.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
